<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$lawrencelry" href="/people/lawrencelry">不鳥萬如一</a>，<strong title="http://ipn.li" class="zu-question-my-bio"><a href="http://ipn.li" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">ipn.li</span><span class="invisible"></span><i class="icon-external"></i></a></strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="42">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$amy-ma-22" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/amy-ma-22" class="zg-link" title="Amy要瘦瘦瘦瘦">Amy要瘦瘦瘦瘦</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$ginvintage" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/ginvintage" class="zg-link" title="Ginvintage">Ginvintage</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="319238" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">‘We saw the Fellini film last Tuesday. It is not one of his best. It lacks a cohesive structure. You know, you get the feeling that he's not absolutely sure what it is he wants to say. 'Course I've always felt he was essentially a ... a technical filmmaker. Granted, <i>La Strada</i> was a great film — great in its use of negative imagery more than anything else. But that simple cohesive core ... you know, it must lead through an artist's work, leading from one to the other. You know what I'm talking about? Like all that <i>Juliet of the Spirits</i> or <i>Satyricon</i>. I found it incredibly indulgent. You know, he really is, he's one of the most indulgent filmmakers ... It's like Samuel Becket — ya know, I admire the technique, but he doesn't, he doesn't hit me on a gut level.’
<a href="/question/20347195/answer/14843332" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
